gw.bizrules.databuilder

Class RuleHeadBuilder<R extends Rule,B extends RuleHeadBuilder<R,B,U>,U extends RuleBuilder<R,U>>

  • java.lang.Object
    • gw.bizrules.databuilder.RuleHeadBuilder<R,B,U>
  • Type Parameters:
    R - Rule subtype
    B - Specific concrete subtype of this superclass
    U - Concrete builder type for specific Rule subtype

    public abstract class RuleHeadBuilder<R extends Rule,B extends RuleHeadBuilder<R,B,U>,U extends RuleBuilder<R,U>>
extends java.lang.Object
    Defines the abstract superclass for concrete subtype builders of a RuleHead. This is not a standard DataBuilder.

        public B withSystemId(java.lang.String systemId)
        Specify the identifier for the system that is responsible for the RuleVersion and Rule that will be the HeadVersion of the created RuleHead. If specified, this overrides the value specified in the RuleBuilder.

      • withStatus

        public B withStatus(RuleStatus ruleStatus)

        ruleStatus - for the HeadVersion of the Rule
